data.description: Check out this raised ranch with 2 bedrooms, 1 bath, and 1 car garage conveniently located close to the Benson District and Dundee. With a little TLC it would be great for a first time homebuyer or investor. The primary bedroom is nice and spacious with plenty of closet space. The fully fenced back yard is a bonus! Call to schedule your showing today!
